- Journal #1992 (arid1a-pancancer-sl-atlas):
  - **Foghorn ARID1B degrader advancing to in vivo PoC 2026.** First-in-class, oral potential, ~5% solid tumors. ARID1A metabolic reprogramming via SLC7A11/glutathione. Eprenetapopt kills SWI/SNF-deficient cells.
- Journal #1994 (rb1-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
