- Journal #1995 (pancancer-ferroptosis-atlas):
  - **FSP1+HDAC inhibitor synergy (Science Advances Jan 2026).** Persister cells depend on FSP1 after GPX4i. HDACi synergizes. FDA-approved HDACi immediately actionable. N6F11 degrades GPX4 cancer-specifically.
